{"tid":1964031,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[Airdrop大法] 係時候要進行FC嘅教育！！","createTime":"2020-04-08T13:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T14:22:44.000Z","uid":72847,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"32ce332b8599d58723d41eb18257c1c00eb13243","tid":1964031,"uid":72847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T13:50:09.000Z","msg":"而家太多fake news，幾乎一日都有幾十單假野四圍係大家呀媽d Whatsapp group度send黎send去，相信作為仔女既我地都收唔少呢d forward messages <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似今日咁，又係度fwd緊所謂「何栢良」講既covid-19資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好想鬧醒呀媽但又知唔怪得佢，因為佢根本就唔識分真假，又唔識fc<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以！！fc呢個技能淨係連登仔識係唔夠嘅，出面仲有好多人都唔知點fc，先搞到fake news四圍傳污煙瘴氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有見及此，我地要做好fc嘅教育！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地可以好似平時share文宣咁，好好善用iphone嘅airdrop function<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 首先去 設定 &gt; 一般 &gt; 關於本機，改返個靚名<br />\n例如叫「fc教學大法」等等，咁人地未收到都get到你想send d咩比佢呀嘛<br />\n<br />\n2. 之後就share 呢三張圖出去<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwtxaSh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwtxaSh.jpg&h=d98a3b78&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cpoxaSi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcpoxaSi.jpg&h=bb8f8b0c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eaBZAiY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeaBZAiY.jpg&h=033d4904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地搭地鐵又可以send，搭巴士又可以send，行超級市場又可以send<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊好好宣揚fc嘅重要性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623889cb7b3fd499cb373c929cd9f8e2c1d